Package: acidic
Title: Power Calculation for Automated Content Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chung-hong", "Chan", , "chainsawtiney@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6232-7530"))
Description: A set of functions for calculating power retained by automated content analytic procedures. This package also contains functions for reproducing the analysis in the paper 'Automated-coerced, increased dilution in correlation' by Chan.
